<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-11 01:06 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2901 &Cx1f; tth-z
r s BC-BKN-THIEL-COLUMN-SPI &LR;      10-11 0892
