</P>
<P>
   SPORTSNIGHT _ Hillary Clinton: the Thinking Man's sex symbol? In
tonight's ``Sports Night'' episode, a main character, Danny, admits
a crush on the first lady and not-yet-announced New York senate
candidate. Pursuing comment from Hillary's campaign - how does it
