pitfalls of shopping in cyberspace.
</P>
<P>
   They also point out that many merchants, too, will be engaging
in e-commerce for the first time. When wet-behind-the-ears shoppers
meet up witlysts say e-tailers are busiest between noon and 3 p.m.
Eastern time because so many office workers surf the Web during
their lunch hour. Adding to that heavy load will only increase the
