   Map of internet companies outside the Washington Beltway.
</P>
<P>
   D.C._Hitech growth -- tk -- (BC-D.C.-HITECH-BOOM-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   Tentative. Fasting growing hitech areas nationwide.
